com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.s3.model

Class MultipartUpload

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.s3.model.MultipartUpload
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MultipartUpload
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A multipart upload is an upload to Amazon S3 that is creating by uploading individual pieces of an object, then telling Amazon S3 to complete the multipart upload and concatenate all the individual pieces together into a single object.
    See Also:
    AmazonS3.initiateMultipartUpload(InitiateMultipartUploadRequest), AmazonS3.uploadPart(UploadPartRequest), AmazonS3.completeMultipartUpload(CompleteMultipartUploadRequest), AmazonS3.abortMultipartUpload(AbortMultipartUploadRequest), Serialized Form
